        <mxCell id="Q-WdIFS8AWOqeyrpqGDp-19" parent="Q-WdIFS8AWOqeyrpqGDp-18" style="shape=note2;boundedLbl=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;size=22;verticalAlign=top;align=left;" value="&lt;ul style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;E-stop: immediate shutdown via ISR and physical power cut; FSM handles follow-up processing&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Endstops and start button: cyclic processing via InputSampler&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Door sensor: immediate software stop via ISR, no physical power cut; FSM handles follow-up processing&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Conectivity Task Low Priority auf Core1&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;PressController als Coordinator auf Core0&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;PWM in Hardware erzeugt&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;MQTT Befehle werden gequeued um vom Controller abgearbeitet zu werden&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;" vertex="1">
